    "Our surroundings are a soft cocoon of culture, history, and beauty, enveloping all who enter in a peaceful contemplation amidst masterpieces.",

    "Leaving the preserved brushstrokes of Impressionist and Post-Impressionist masters behind, we step back outside. With a brief walk through Paris's storied streets, our footsteps echoing gently on the cobblestone, we find ourselves at the entrance to the Jardin des Tuileries." /
